<paragraph blockId="72.[151,1437,151,679]" pageId="72" pageNumber="73">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,380,151,176]" inLineHeading="true" pageId="72" pageNumber="73" reason="1">Male genitalia.</emphasis>
Pygofer in lateral view large, triangulate, caudodorsal process long, robust, small elongate caudoventral process reduced to lobe below base of caudodorsal process (
<figureCitation box="[1004,1105,188,212]" captionStart="FIGURES 277–284" captionStartId="70.[151,264,1942,1965]" captionTargetBox="[216,1352,182,1911]" captionTargetId="figure-72@70.[200,1387,177,1922]" captionTargetPageId="70" captionText="FIGURES 277–284. Docalidia zahniseri, sp. nov. (277) pygofer, lateral view; (278) right subgenital plate, ventral view; (279) right style, lateral view; (280) right style, dorsal view; (281) aedeagus and dorsal connective, lateral view; (282) aedeagus, ventral view; (283) connective, caudal view; (284) dorsal connective, dorsal view." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5281813" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5281813/files/figure.png" pageId="72" pageNumber="73">Fig. 277</figureCitation>
); right subgenital plate long, outer lateral margin broadly convex, glabrous (
<figureCitation box="[673,771,223,247]" captionStart="FIGURES 277–284" captionStartId="70.[151,264,1942,1965]" captionTargetBox="[216,1352,182,1911]" captionTargetId="figure-72@70.[200,1387,177,1922]" captionTargetPageId="70" captionText="FIGURES 277–284. Docalidia zahniseri, sp. nov. (277) pygofer, lateral view; (278) right subgenital plate, ventral view; (279) right style, lateral view; (280) right style, dorsal view; (281) aedeagus and dorsal connective, lateral view; (282) aedeagus, ventral view; (283) connective, caudal view; (284) dorsal connective, dorsal view." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5281813" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5281813/files/figure.png" pageId="72" pageNumber="73">Fig. 278</figureCitation>
); style long, longer than aedeagus, very robust, inflated apically with U-shaped row of short setae in dorsal view, digitate process apically (Figs. 298, 280); aedeagus robust, broadly sinuate in lateral view, twisted medially in ventral view, small sharp spine near middle, gonopore distad of spine (
<figureCitation box="[226,393,332,356]" captionStart="FIGURES 277–284" captionStartId="70.[151,264,1942,1965]" captionTargetBox="[216,1352,182,1911]" captionTargetId="figure-72@70.[200,1387,177,1922]" captionTargetPageId="70" captionText="FIGURES 277–284. Docalidia zahniseri, sp. nov. (277) pygofer, lateral view; (278) right subgenital plate, ventral view; (279) right style, lateral view; (280) right style, dorsal view; (281) aedeagus and dorsal connective, lateral view; (282) aedeagus, ventral view; (283) connective, caudal view; (284) dorsal connective, dorsal view." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5281813" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5281813/files/figure.png" pageId="72" pageNumber="73">Figs. 281, 282</figureCitation>
); connective, broadly T-shaped, apex of arms curved anteriorly, membranous below anterior arms, narrow median ridge present, stem long (
<figureCitation box="[680,779,367,391]" captionStart="FIGURES 277–284" captionStartId="70.[151,264,1942,1965]" captionTargetBox="[216,1352,182,1911]" captionTargetId="figure-72@70.[200,1387,177,1922]" captionTargetPageId="70" captionText="FIGURES 277–284. Docalidia zahniseri, sp. nov. (277) pygofer, lateral view; (278) right subgenital plate, ventral view; (279) right style, lateral view; (280) right style, dorsal view; (281) aedeagus and dorsal connective, lateral view; (282) aedeagus, ventral view; (283) connective, caudal view; (284) dorsal connective, dorsal view." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5281813" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5281813/files/figure.png" pageId="72" pageNumber="73">Fig. 283</figureCitation>
); dorsal connective, short, broadly basally, tapered distally (
<figureCitation box="[159,258,404,428]" captionStart="FIGURES 277–284" captionStartId="70.[151,264,1942,1965]" captionTargetBox="[216,1352,182,1911]" captionTargetId="figure-72@70.[200,1387,177,1922]" captionTargetPageId="70" captionText="FIGURES 277–284. Docalidia zahniseri, sp. nov. (277) pygofer, lateral view; (278) right subgenital plate, ventral view; (279) right style, lateral view; (280) right style, dorsal view; (281) aedeagus and dorsal connective, lateral view; (282) aedeagus, ventral view; (283) connective, caudal view; (284) dorsal connective, dorsal view." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5281813" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5281813/files/figure.png" pageId="72" pageNumber="73">Fig. 284</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
